<p><div class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 240px">
	<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/22007612@N05/4393557478" title="Glenn Beck"><img title="Glenn Beck" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4066/4393557478_5dd0b569a4_m.jpg" alt="Glenn Beck" width="240" height="160" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Image by Gage Skidmore via Flickr</p>
</div></p>
</div>
<blockquote><p>What America is, to me, is a guy doesn&#8217;t want to buy, you let him not buy, you respect his not buying. A guy has a crazy notion different from your crazy notion, you pat him on the back and say hey, pal, <a href='http://092.me'>nice</a> crazy notion, let&#8217;s go have a beer. America to me should be shouting all the time, a bunch of shouting voices, most of them wrong, some of them nuts, but, please, not just one droning glamorous reasonable voice.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">&#8211; George Saunders, &#8220;My Flamboyant Grandson&#8221; in <em><a href="https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/associates/network/build-links/individual/simple-get-html.html?ie=UTF8&amp;assoc_ss_ref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2F159448242X%3Fie%3DUTF8%26ref_%3Dtmm_pap_title_0&amp;asin=159448242X&amp;parentASIN=159448242X">In Persuasion Nation</a></em></p>
</blockquote>
